choices.text:
inevitably trying to decide what colorful earrings best compliment my right underarm’s beauty spot.

Like Dot above, I always thought I was destined to be such a fierce dominatrix, until a good male friend pointed out the reality was I was actually more likely set to be his bossy lesbian partner. I have to say I could completely understand and sympathize with his past relationship with me involving both roles.

(Well played Gully….truly well played!)

Here is where healthcare and policing the my friend Maeve’s mother’s life skills would finally come together. Being bossy and curious forces a person to research like crazy on how to tackle a problem. And speaking of research and tackling, how many times have your close friends researched how to play better tetris, replacing your applications on your phone you would never use? Well, that is what my adult brain has been reduced too, even screen cleaning; but that is discussion for another day.

So, what if I was to go to a casting company and see if I could get on a reality show.

For the record, the idea is NOT to test my quiet assertive strength. This has been my hangup with televised stress tests. I know family, it is not reasonable to believe I do not have anything interesting to say.
